":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"我開到呀。<br />\n但我冇大陸電話。搞唔到ebanking<br />\n<br />\n我好少番大陸, 所以用唔著電話<br />\n<br />\n有冇好方法或者平plan 可以用先比錢 唔用唔駛錢"},{"pid":"fae467024da0a2668f82d4acf1c9c10828ed9d0c","tid":331140,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"68a8f5248f71b82532d448dbd4b07284118aff95","tid":331140,"uid":113914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 深圳邊到有得出電話卡？見你地講到10分鐘就有卡 好吸引"},{"pid":"91b6f552a8917fe0b790e1220e8cafe9e656b707","tid":331140,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"一卡兩號"},{"pid":"bc0149047061bf88d593df76430ad5bd0df37511","tid":331140,"uid":59563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 深圳邊到有得出電話卡？見你地講到10分鐘就有卡 好吸引</blockquote><br />\n我都係去咗福民中移動間營業廳度搞<br />\n因為要實名，街檔做唔到，要去營業廳"}]}